title: Enochville Fire & Rescue

review.description: Thank you to the guys that responded today to the dog attack on Christy Circle. You guys were so quick. At the time it s...eemed like forever but I know it wasn't. I also want to apologize...
I would like to say thank you to all the firefighters and police that came out to help put out the fire we were trying to burn.All of you were very nice and glad to have a great fire dept!
